<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DSA Practice Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0eafc 0%, #cfdef3 100%);
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .dashboard-header {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .dashboard-description {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card-container {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .card-custom {
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .card-custom:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
    <nav>
        <%- include('../partials/nav',{isLoggedIn}) %>
    </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="dashboard-header text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Your DSA Practice Dashboard</h1>
            <p class="lead">Track your progress, challenge yourself, and master data structures and algorithms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dashboard-description text-center">
            <p>Our platform provides a curated list of problems to help you build a strong foundation. From fundamental concepts like arrays and linked lists to advanced topics like dynamic programming and graph algorithms, we've got you covered. <br>Start your journey today by logging in or signing up!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/home" class="btn btn-lg btn-success">Start Practicing</a>
            </div>
        <div class="row card-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-custom shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-muted">Total Problems</h5>
                        <h2 class="card-text display-3 text-primary">500+</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Explore a vast library of problems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-custom shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-muted">Difficulty Levels</h5>
                        <h2 class="card-text display-3 text-success">Easy, Medium, Hard</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Practice at your own pace.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-custom shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-muted">Featured Topics</h5>
                        <h2 class="card-text display-4 text-warning">Arrays, Trees, Graphs</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Deep dive into key data structures.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
